task.summary: Created an intitializeGameEnv method in the initial view controller to refactor a bit since there was a lot of duplicated code. This method will load the gameenv FXML file set the stage and it will take a board and pass that to the FXMLGameenv controller constructor. Then this method will set the controller to the FXML file since the file does not specify a controller.

Cleaned up the files a bit. Deleted the FXMLGUI controller that wasnt being used. Files deleted: FXMLGuiController, NewTicTacToeBoard, extra FXML GameEnv file. Moved the FXML files to the resources folder.
Modified Player class. Created PlayerProfile class in utility. Will create json object and export to json file. Work in progress

Created player profile in utility. Handles writing and reading json player files. Json file will have player name, wins and losses. A static PlayerProfile is created in Main. Player class was modified.
created a jars folder and added json-simple jar and mapped the dependencies

modified tictactoe engine to increment wins and losses. Modified tictactoe to implement bge.Player instead of its own. All other engines or board or logic should implement or use the player class. I made it Static in main for testing but there will only exist two players.
